main event: A UFO was reported hovering and flashing lights in Quincy, Washington on September 9, 1962, with a piece of metal found the following day potentially associated with the sighting.
interesting points: The caller described the object as flashing lights and hovering for 3-4 seconds, there was a physical piece of metal found that was analyzed, the material was identified as type 3003, the sighting was corroborated by local media reports and other witnesses, weather conditions were reported as scattered clouds.
sighted object: a bright light object hovering and flashing
witness description: various personnel including local radio reporters and civilians
